events.name: Coyote Hackathon 2013
events.about:
Where: 2405 Siebel

When: Feb 15-16th from 8pm-8am.  Judging will begin at 8:15am.  

Rules: Teams of up to three people can sign up!

Prizes: 

  • 1st - Nexus 10 and Coyote visit  the opportunity to have lunch with execs
  • 2nd - Nexus 7
  • 3rd - $50 Amazon gift cards
  • Everyone will get swag
Dinner, snacks, and breakfast will be provided!
